{"tid":221211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒大球迷發聯署聲明割蓆　稱舉港毒橫額者非球迷會會員","createTime":"2017-04-28T14:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:57:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55f42305d82e03ac1e95a3d227190f71f2d3aea6","tid":221211,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"早前在旺角大球場舉行的亞冠盃比賽，東方龍獅主場對廣州恒大，期間有廣州恒大球迷舉起「殲英犬滅港毒」帶有政治意味的橫額。亞洲足協昨日發聲明，正式起訴廣州恒大，指其球迷違反了該協會的紀律守則，廣州恒大及肇事球迷都會面臨懲處。<br />\n<br />\n今日（4月28日）有20間中國球迷會發表聯署聲明，指經調查後，肇事的4名球迷不是任何球迷會成員，指各球迷會不知4人的身份，對事件亦不知情，希望亞洲足協深入調查事件，不要傷害中國球迷感情。<br />\n<br />\n有關聲明由名為「佛山球迷聯盟」的官方微博，在今日中午約12時半發布，並有20間球迷會作聯署。聲明內容指，在4月25日，325名廣州球迷在香港旺角大球場的指定客隊球迷區內，觀看東方與廣州恒大的賽事，並留意到亞洲足協收到報告，指有廣州球迷舉起涉嫌有政治內容的橫額，聲明指對此深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"a03e8e0704600731cf0800967b44ef816f78b255","tid":221211,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"不要傷害中國XX感情真係萬能key"},{"pid":"674233c58dbf5c092db13fac44b970c9b2e37c75","tid":221211,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"下次屌支那國歌就話場外屌，場內球迷無出過聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b1e78649946ca4141530091373055c47a214aa","tid":221211,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffca4538d472aeced3b50641f01120b319f7ee6e","tid":221211,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e93dda996911635f5a10f4a8f845e1360745a51","tid":221211,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}